				<td colspan="2"><span>2kpp isn't too bad for those.  You can Chant Kite hill giants in Rathe Mountains for nice coin at your level.  If you can manage to charm a second while you chant, you will kill them even faster, though the risk goes way up.
<br />

<br />
Sell fine steel and stuff to the gnome gem vendor at the inn.  If you get loaded up with coppers, rather than run back to PoK to bank, just buy one Peridot at a time to eat up your coppers.  You can use them later for bumming temp or virtue off clerics, and it is better than destroying coppers or wasting time running to the bank.</span></td>
